### 1. Register a NEW Admin User (Change email if you run this again!)
# @name register
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Super Admin",
  "email": "admin_new_02@cinemaverse.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "0999999999",
  "role": "admin"
}

### 2. Login (Automatically captures the token)
# @name login
POST http://localhost:5000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin_new_02@cinemaverse.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Create a Movie (Uses the token from Step 2)
POST http://localhost:5000/admin/movies
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "The Matrix 4",
  "description": "Neo returns...",
  "director": "Lana Wachowski",
  "duration": 148,
  "releaseDate": "2021-12-22",
  "posterUrl": "https://example.com/matrix.jpg",
  "trailerUrl": "https://example.com/trailer.mp4"
}

### 4. Create a Cinema (Uses the token from Step 2)
POST http://localhost:5000/admin/cinemas
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Downtown Cinema",
  "address": "123 Main St, Metropolis",
  "description": "The best cinema in town."
}

### 5. Create a Room in the Cinema (Uses the token from Step 2)
POST http://localhost:5000/admin/cinemas/1/rooms  
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Room 1",
  "cinemaId": 1,
  "totalSeats": 150
}

### 6. Create a Showtime for the Movie in the Room (Uses the token from Step 2)
POST http://localhost:5000/admin/showtimes
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "movieId": 1,
  "roomId": 1,
  "startTime": "2024-07-01T19:00:00",
  "endTime": "2024-07-01T21:30:00",
  "basePrice": 50000
}

### 7. Get Seats for the Showtime (Uses the token from Step 2)
GET http://localhost:5000/admin/showtimes/1/seats 
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. Add Seats to the Showtime (Uses the token from Step 2)
POST http://localhost:5000/admin/showtimes/1/seats
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seatIds": [1, 2, 3, 4, 5],
  "price": 60000
} 

### 9. Change Seat Status in the Showtime (Uses the token from Step 2)
PUT http://localhost:5000/admin/showtimes/1/seats/1 
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "LOCKED"
}

### 10. Remove a Seat from the Showtime (Uses the token from Step 2)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/admin/showtimes/1/seats/3  
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. Create a Booking (Uses the token from Step 2)
POST http://localhost:5000/admin/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "showtimeId": 1,
  "totalPrice": 120000,
  "paymentMethod": "CREDIT_CARD"
}

### 11. Add Seats to a Booking (Uses the token from Step 2)
POST http://localhost:5000/admin/bookings/2/seats 
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "seatIds": [1, 2]
}

### 12. Remove a Seat from a Booking (Uses the token from Step 2)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/admin/bookings/2/seats/2 
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 13. GET booking details (Uses the token from Step 2)  
GET http://localhost:5000/admin/bookings/2
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 14. Get summerized list of all bookings in month (Uses the token from Step 2)
GET http://localhost:5000/admin/bookings/summary?month=12&year=2025
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json  

